The Adventure Pass includes access to download episodes six (available now!), seven, and eight, as they become available, starting in Summer 2016.
These new episodes continue the story of the New Order of the Stone, following Jesse and the group as they explore uncharted worlds beyond their own.
Requires purchase and installation of Minecraft: Story Mode; not included in the Adventure Pass.
